"nj" = (
/obj/item/paper/djstation{
	info = "The ship has gone to hell! I don't know what happened but there's just so much SHIT in the halls now! They picked the crew off so quickly. The radios have gone silent now, I think me and the guys are the last ones left. Thankfully we managed to seal off the medical wing, none of the shitstorm outside can get in here now.<br><br>While we were barricading ourselves in here, my assistant managed to blow up a pair of demons that tried to rush in using an improvised explosive, I managed to recover their brains. We're going to put them into cyborg bodies, and once we verify they work, we'll arm them to the teeth and use them to take back the ship! Karma, baby!<br><br>Update: FUCK! They're bad! They managed to override their laws! I'm locked in here with them! They've not noticed me yet thankfully, they can't see through these frosted windows. If you're reading this, you need to send help before- oh no! NO! They found me! Get away! GET THE FUCK AWAY! NOOOO! AAAAAAAGGGGGHHHHHHHHhHhhhhhhh...<br><br><i>The rest of the paper is too bloodstained to make out.</i>";
	name = "Bloodstained note"
	},
/turf/simulated/floor/plasteel/dark{
	baseturf = /turf/simulated/floor/plating
	},
/area/ruin/space/powered)
